Package com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractExtractor
    Extracts an element from the WebResponse in the Context.
    CookieExtractor
    Extracts the specified cookie from the headers located in Context.getWebResponse().
    CookieExtractorTest
    Tests for CookieExtractor
    ExtractorTest
    Abstract class for extractor tests.
    HeaderExtractor
    Extracts all headers with the name provided by AbstractExtractor.getExtractionExpression().
    HeaderExtractorTest
    Tests for HeaderExtractor
    RegexpExtractor
    Matches the pattern provided via AbstractExtractor.getExtractionExpression() and applies it to the LightWeightPage.getContent() which is created with the Context.getWebResponse().
    RegexpExtractorTest
    Tests for RegexpExtractor
